{"tid":35204,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【尊重跨性別者】唔用「he」和「she」 牛津籲用性別中立代名詞「ze」","createTime":"2016-12-12T02:36:59.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-14T04:01:37.000Z","uid":54337,"like":3,"dislike":56,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ed539f9b79cc54f2e6b762b5d8b28a3dc2ab5801","tid":35204,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T02:36:59.000Z","msg":"【尊重跨性別者】唔用「he」和「she」 牛津籲用性別中立代名詞「ze」<br />\n<br />\n英國牛津大學鼓勵性別多元，呼籲學生用代名詞「ze」取代he和she，以免得失跨性別學生。<br />\n<br />\n牛津大學最具影響力學生社團辯論學會（Oxford Union）在宣傳單張中表示，希望將「ze」的應用推廣至課堂上。<br />\n<br />\n根據牛津大學的行為守則，用錯代名詞界定跨性別人士是違反守則。<br />\n<br />\n爭取LGBT（同性戀、雙性戀及跨性別）權益人士塔切爾（Peter Tatchell）認為，淡化性別差疑和障礙是好事，亦認為性別中立代名詞值得鼓勵，但毋須強制使用。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb29353d27f6939ba6b8c8aaf8eaa3bb25e697f5","tid":35204,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T02:38:08.000Z","msg":"戇撚鳩"},{"pid":"337494745aed2c57d9b199e0dd278c2ebd6840fa","tid":35204,"uid":52651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T02:40:06.000Z","msg":"多撚魚"},{"pid":"395245473efa0f2f454c19783a6f6ab0d94ea563","tid":35204,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T02:40:19.000Z","msg":"扮法國人定德國人口音<br />\n而家大陸都成日用ta包括他同她"},{"pid":"48d9e29a5eb1fe985b9402e0dd068d8aa84fd5da","tid":35204,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T02:42:53.000Z","msg":"要正常人就返啲唔正常嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b627614d95d293961f2f370293322b36e46b1f37","tid":35204,"uid":4324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T02:44:04.000Z","msg":"姐 is not a girl"},{"pid":"6da7f8f6e2b02beae0542e9a5cb2c9510421e67d","tid":35204,"uid":49136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T02:45:27.000Z","msg":"香港=「佢」"},{"pid":"a0f734827912d8a05b9d919c9fbe20f556282480"