quote><br />\n<br />\n讀寫障礙？<br />\n人地話跟性器官決定用he/she,因為呢個係基因係客觀事實，如果跟主觀心理既咁一個人既性別可以變黎變去，今日係男聽日係女都得所以為呢班人定一個字係多鳩餘<br />\n<br />\n除非有啲人天生又有撚又有西先有資格用ze形容、但呢啲例子幾千萬一都唔知有無一個<br />\n<br />\n到最後原來都係為左同志自我感覺良好要全世界就佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一早話呢個世界不嬲同志特權"},{"pid":"dabfebe2b682feac30ac0459f679f0a9e5ea50a8","tid":35204,"uid":5574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T04:42:48.000Z","msg":"發溫....<br />\n同推 gender X 一撚樣柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個撚個transgender 都係某啲痴線鐘意&quot;話&quot; 自己無性別攪另類既咩...."},{"pid":"60f6d1fd41f4d18bf8d5c7cae9fe7f07d6420a98","tid":35204,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T04:46:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a2ab2bd95ee8903784fcbce8888209917d3d064","tid":35204,"uid":4052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T04:55:42.000Z","msg":"我想問ze點讀"},{"pid":"9c6c1a81820019df63b9770bae93d3fbc5ad9780","tid":35204,"uid":35317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T04:56:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>除非真係個人天生有閪又有鳩(或者兩樣都無)，如果唔係有咩需要用呢個字?<br />\n<br />\n變左性既咪用變左之後個性別囉，eg.你男變女都係想做女人，咁咪如你所願用she<br />\n<br />\n個啲咩心理認為自己係女人就收皮啦，你天生有鳩有架啦，你諗下就可以變男人咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為自己心理上接受唔到現實,就要全世界另外99.99999%人虛構個&quot;第三性&quot;就佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n用基因(XX/XY chromosome)黎定義性別根本唔會有ambiguous case</blockquote><br />\n學術討論<br />\n咁XXY點計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nX好似係dominant allele?"},{"pid":"e14e4468bedef7cda31ae8819a2c3bf597c0f3d8","tid":35204,"uid":35317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T04:57:04.000Z","